### Gallery

These example images have been generated using the pepper's built-in
reports.  The output type has been set to `svg` in order to render both
thumbnails and high-resolution versions of each plot after wards. The
latter can be accessed by clicking on a thumbnail image.

The repository data is from [pepper's own git
repository](http://github.com/jgehring/pepper)
as well as from the self-hosting repositories of
[Git](http://git.kernel.org/?p=git/git.git;a=summary) and
[Mercurial](http://selenic.com/repo/hg). Additionally,
a clone of [Linus Torvald's kernel
tree](http://git.kernel.org/?p=linux/kernel/git/torvalds/linux-2.6.git;a=summary)
has been used.

